Predict Likelihood to Add Assets for Wealth Management Analytics
Financial advisors can intelligently forecast the likelihood of adding assets to accounts using this app.
It prescribes actions on how to increase the chances to grow your account assets.
Note: This app is included with CRM Analytics for Financial Services, available at an extra charge.
title: Predicting Asset Growth in Wealth Management
